      "content": "That \"creativity\" is exactly the problem though. Management feels like it's too much of a wildcard. They aren't looking for \"unique\" solutions, they just want standard answers delivered at a fraction of the cost. The decision is pretty much final, so there isn't really a way to \"integrate\" you into a system that's designed to replace your entire function.",
